Package org.infinispan.xsite.statetransfer

Class NoOpXSiteStateProvider

java.lang.Object
org.infinispan.xsite.statetransfer.NoOpXSiteStateProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
XSiteStateProvider
public class NoOpXSiteStateProvider extends Object implements XSiteStateProvider
A no-op implementation of XSiteStateProvider.

This class is used when cross-site replication is disabled.

Since:
10.0
Author:
Pedro Ruivo
